{"tid":1965268,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【踢保/續保/走得甩手足請入】狗開始拉返踢保手足 (暫時去到10月中)","createTime":"2020-04-09T11:04:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T14:46:17.000Z","uid":40542,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e661d33c3995bfa698001b61147b12b3a03190b6","tid":1965268,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:04:09.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟留意到最近每日上庭嘅新案件（我嘅定義：唔係之前排期，亦都唔係最近48小時被捕過堂嘅案件），都係曾經<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">踢保/正在續保/走得甩無事</span></ins></strong>手足嘅案件。<br />\n<br />\n小弟做咗少少資料整合，發現去到4月頭（今日），警察同律政司暫時拉到<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">10月中</span></ins></strong>踢保/續保/走得甩手足（check CCTV)，而呢兩日嘅新案件爲：1012 柴灣 及 1013 屯門嘅手足。<br />\n<br />\n政府暫時主要都係做<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">攻擊性武器/襲警</span></ins></strong>嘅新案件，亦都有零星其他類型案件（非法集結，管有可作非法用途工具罪，抗拒在正當執行職務的警務人員，在公眾地方造成阻礙罪等）。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>請有關手足注意以下幾點：</ins></strong><br />\n1. 做足心理準備，自己有機會進入漫長嘅司法過程（仲有約6000個踢保或續保手足未告，其實港共點都會落charge，只係時間問題，加上律政司將會增聘人手處理，所以心理準備一定要有）<br />\n2. 執屋<br />\n3. 背定律師電話<br />\n4. 電話洗機（係成部reset過，tg都開過個新，del msg 係無用的）<br />\n5. 電話改密碼 (15個位以上，最好唔係英文詞語，因爲會方便咗Cellebrite去撞密碼 ［狗破解電話嘅app］）<br />\n6. 電腦改密碼，最好加密埋個harddisk (Mac機記得要開File Vault)<br />\n7. 諗到再講<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>小弟整合咗嘅新案件表</strong></ins><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1ibU1I4uTpvwdyQGgSx2cX8G--D4EYOmFc7bSKqLAeXU/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1ibU1I4uTpvwdyQGgSx2cX8G--D4EYOmFc7bSKqLAeXU%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVTBezIcYxRdZTJmtLZSysqE%3D&h=0aaf2552\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1ibU1I4uTpvwdyQGgSx2cX8G--D4EYOmFc7bSKqLAeXU/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n香港獨立，唯一出路</span>"},{"pid":"0f7b6eaed5f9b144c7cc886b6159177c6ac96089","tid":1965268,"uid":40542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:05:44.000Z","msg":"另外其他人，請養成良好習慣，<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">每晚臨訓前都睇被捕人士關注組</span></span></strong></ins>，睇吓自己有無時間去聽審聲援。<br />\n<br />\n趕唔切去唔使怕遲到，<br />\n唔使還押嘅手足需要大家嘅遮陣護送，<br />\n還押手足需要大家送車。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n被捕人士關注組tg channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/s/youarenotalonehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fs%2Fyouarenotalonehk&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVTBezIcYxRdZTJmtLZSysqE%3D&h=0a765f60\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/s/youarenotalonehk</a><br />\n<br />\nig<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fyouarenotalonehk&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVTBezIcYxRdZTJmtLZSysqE%3D&h=d0f24071\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk</a><br />\n<br />\n法庭文字直播台（去唔到嘅都唔該睇吓直播，關心吓手足）<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVTBezIcYxRdZTJmtLZSysqE%3D&h=ca2decc2\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live</a>"},{"pid":"23efe59d21eb902bf8c09337245e890cdc3ac480","tid":1965268,"uid":108146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:05:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"290664d24cbbc5617fb33274e6470fa29472b772","tid":1965268,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:06:18.000Z","msg":"請幫手推俾手足睇到呢個po"},{"pid":"ee6f23f5f8458421ac270e30b39a8a1f7408b145","tid":1965268,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:06:42.000Z","msg":"請幫手推俾手足睇到呢個po<br />\n要正皮同留言先推到上熱門"},{"pid":"788343b84695e5e54326cfef6f0331792c6ad839","tid":1965268,"uid":40542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:09:01.000Z","msg":"攻擊性武器/襲警手足你哋一定要做好準備！<br />\n但其實警察好快就會做次一級嘅案件（非法集結等），所以所有俾狗咬過嘅手足，真係要做好心理準備。"},{"pid":"c80e0354abaace0cb7255e6746b84e41d5d38e22","tid":1